  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the middle class, if you would look in an apartment there how they lived, it was always clean, but the kitchen with a room or those that have the small stores they had a kitchen, a little kitchen in the room in the back and the front was the store, and this was their whole living quarters.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were considered mostly the middle class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, some who were even better off and that could probably afford more, but they had it from their parents already and it went like this without, without any trying harder to get any better because he wasn't used to any better.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a few who were considered rich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You want to know, I'll tell you a little episode.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if it may interest you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day-- you know [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nittel, ?] what [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nittel ?] is?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There is one day that-- it's a sort of a strong [NON-ENGLISH], a strong traditional-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] traditional-- It's a custom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--acceptance that one day we're not allowed practically to learn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we, this we-- we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people-- play a little cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was one man who was married in to the richest man in-- in town, so he was considered-- he was a very intelligent man.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was considered-- he was a very rich man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He invited us to come up to his house to play cards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just tell it to you because I just remind myself talking about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had played cards-- it was a Saturday night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the only time that religious people played cards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in, in the middle, he got hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
